features: Materials: Vehomy dog bandanas are made of cotton and polyester, reversible materials, durable and breathable, touch soft and comfortable. The pet hat clip is made of hard paper and mental, could provide your pet dog or cat a beautiful and different dressing up on Valentine's Day.

Sizes: The size of the heart bandana is 48*48*70cm / 19*19*27inches, the height of the pet hat is 4cm / 1.57inches x diameter 10cm / 3.94inches, which are suitable for small medium large dogs and cats.

Lovely design: our pet bandanas are themed on Valentine's Day, featuring various heart shapes, using red and pink colors, full of sweet and romantic flavor, wearing them makes your pets more beautiful and lovely.

Wide applications: this puppy neck scarfs could be worn around pet's neck as a scarf or put on the back and head as a beautiful outfit and hat, also suitable for young people as ties, scarves, headbands and so on, various usages and practical.
Package includes: you will get 1 piece of pink sweet dog neck scarf which is printed heart pattern and a red hair hat clip.
